Programming 5 assignment


===================================================================
Shader wrote on site : shdr.bkcore.com. shader link is below:

http://shdr.bkcore.com/#

===================================================================

Shader best applied on sphere or cube.

Done all the basics requriments and fancy stuff.
fancy stuff:
1. Light direction changes based on normal's direction of ech pixel.
2. Vertex shaders rotates the object in X,Y,Z direction.
3. Fragment shaders gives wave and stripes pattern to object. It uses procedural texture to color object.

=================================================================

Included v1.txt for vertex shader and p1.txt for fragment shader in case there is some problem with abve link.





